On FreeBSD:

  sudo pkg install rubygem-plist rubygem-rake rubygem-virtus daemontools entr
  sudo rake install

  edit /etc/pf.conf and add two anchors in the appropriate sections:

    nat-anchor launchd.nat
    rdr-anchor launchd.rdr


On Debian or related systems like Ubuntu:

	sudo apt-get install ruby-plist ruby-virtus
